title: Breaking Down the Brendan, Pieper, and Natasha Drama From 'Bachelor in Paradise.' Plus: ‘Big Brother,’ ‘Real Housewives of Salt Lake City,’ and ‘The Circle’ | Reality Top 5
description:
This Friday, Juliet and Callie get into all the details of the developments of the Brendan, Pieper, and Natasha drama from ‘Bachelor in Paradise’ (0:30) and Callie tells Juliet about the incredible strategies at play in the final episodes of ‘Big Brother’ (20:05). Then they get into all the legal drama from ‘Real Housewives of Beverly Hills’ (30:30) and the ‘Real Housewives of Salt Lake City’ trailer (37:40). Finally, they talk about ‘The Circle’ Season 3 and ‘Titletown High’ on Netflix (44:30).
Hosts: Juliet Litman and Callie Curry
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
